    "step_id": "8e1a1f04-218b-46a7-a657-a7951ff51ed1",
    "description": "<p id=\"isPasted\">👣 Follow These Steps 👣</p><p><br></p><p>⚡&nbsp;Trigger&nbsp;⚡</p><ol start=\"1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-family: \"Inter var\", helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);' type=\"1\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></li></ol><p>🔨 Inspire SOPs 🔨</p><p>This is the final checks and reviews before the job is generated for manufacture.&nbsp;</p><ol style='box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-family: \"Inter var\", helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Ensure all materials and hardware are correct and appropriate for the intended use</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Review all cabinets and ensure no anomalies in:<ul><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Size</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Shape&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Handle ware</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Feet placement&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li>Review colours are consistent with renders and quote</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Ensure all materials and hardware are correct as per the quote.&nbsp;</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Review the Materials in Jobman alongside the Mozaik BOM and add any additional components to the BOM in Jobman&nbsp;</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Select source</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">In popup window deselect \"Order in Transit\"&nbsp;</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">In popup window select source.</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Generate the following:<ul><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Info Sheet</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">BOM&nbsp;</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Patterns&nbsp;</li><li id=\"isPasted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Job Brief&nbsp;</li></ul></li><li>Save the generated docs in the \"Manufacturing\" folder of the <strong>Workorder </strong>Sharepoint folder.</li><li>Optimise Cut patterns in Mozaik Optimiser</li><li>Review and adjust to ensure no smaller panels are at risk of damage due to being too close to edges.&nbsp;</li><li>Generate G-Code in Mozaik Optimiser</li></ol><p>⏰ Expected Timelines ⏰</p><p>Within 48hours of design review&nbsp;</p>",
