  {
    "id": "c76403a3-b295-416d-8e51-622fb1c0b476",
    "name": "🪄 Create Deliverables",
    "step_id": "8e1a1f04-218b-46a7-a657-a7951ff51ed1",
    "description": "<p id=\"isPasted\">👣 Follow These Steps 👣</p><p><br></p><p>🔨 Inspire SOPs 🔨</p><ol style='box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-family: \"Inter var\", helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Navigate to work order</li><li>Navigate to the SharePoint folder for the work order and open the <strong>Infosheet</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>using the <strong>PDF Gear</strong>, PDF reader.</li><li>In the PDF Gear reader navigate to \"Tools\" &gt; \"Convert\"&gt; \"PDF to Excel\"</li><li>Select Convert in Pop up window, this will then save it to your downloads folder.</li><li>Open the Excel sheet and delete the top 3 rows for better viewability.&nbsp;</li><li>Navigate to Jobman Workorder &gt; Resources &gt; Deliverables &gt; Import</li><li>Select Jobman as the driver then select Import</li><li>Download the Sample CSV and Open it (it will be saved in your downloads folder)</li><li>Review this Loom Video <a href=\"https://www.loom.com/share/316bf463411446c2939dabd7ed610bce\">here</a></li><li>With both the converted Excel Infosheet and the Sample CSV open transfer the information from the infosheet to the Sample CSV&nbsp;</li><li>Navigate to Work order &gt; Resources &gt; Materials&nbsp;</li><li>Using the Snipping tool take a screen grab of the Materials Name column&nbsp;</li><li>Using the text extraction function in Snipping tool copy the text</li><li>Paste this text into the Sample CSV Name column</li><li>Navigate back to the work order materials screen and take a screen grab of the quantities of the materials items.</li><li id=\"isPasted\">Using the text extraction function in Snipping tool copy the text</li><li>Paste this text into the Sample CSV Description column</li><li>In the Sample CSV remove blank, edge tape and board rows.&nbsp;</li><li>Save the Sample CSV sheet.&nbsp;</li><li>Navigate back to the Work order Deliverables&gt; import&nbsp;</li><li>Drag and drop this sample CSV into the \"Import Deliverables\" drop box.</li></ol><p>⏰ Expected Timelines ⏰</p><p>Within 24 hours of Finalising BOM</p>",
    "organisation_id": "fbc41182-dffc-4597-ab02-462388d6a239",
