    "description": "<p id=\"isPasted\">👣 Follow These Steps 👣</p><p><br></p><p>⚡&nbsp;Trigger&nbsp;⚡</p><ol start=\"1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-family: \"Inter var\", helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);' type=\"1\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></li></ol><p>🔨 Inspire SOPs 🔨</p><ol><li>Review Picking list&nbsp;</li><li>Pick all material items required as per picking list</li><li>Label all Material Items with the job number and name.&nbsp;</li><li>Centralise all hardware and components in picking shelves</li><li>Centralise all board and tape in cut prep rack in Factory (ensure label is visible from the front)&nbsp;</li></ol><p><em>NOTE: if stock is not physically on location, ensure on receipt that it is labelled and centralised with the other elements of the Job.&nbsp;</em></p><p>⏰ Expected Timelines ⏰</p><p>Within 24 hours of Finalising BOM</p>",
